      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "诸葛暗上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "六幺令",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "昏昏度年，终日长街东走西穿。生涯只靠课儿钱。嚼得着，叫神仙，口儿打诨将人骗，口儿打诨将人骗。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "我诸葛暗。自从放走洪秀才，恐怕有啥是非轮到我身上来，不敢出去做生意，等拉屋里吃，吃得筋疲力尽。现在打听打听，勿听见说起载，只好原出去做做生意，摆张桌子在官井头，生意到呒啥。二老官！",
      "text_length": 90
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "老官"
      ],
      "text": "先生！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "桌子阿摆好拉里哉？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "老官"
      ],
      "text": "摆好仔半日哉！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "今朝生意好点么，多把两个铜钱俚哉！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小厮甲、小厮乙同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "六幺令",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "忙寻瓦砖，惹得痴儿戏耍来顽。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "痴丫头！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "萧惜芬上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧惜芬"
      ],
      "text": "做什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "六幺令",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "阴沟爬出灶中眠。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "阿吃糕？微微笑，把头点，",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧惜芬"
      ],
      "text": "吃的，拿来㖸！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "六幺令",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "牙儿嚼断难吞咽，牙儿嚼断难吞咽。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "打，打，打！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小厮甲、小厮乙同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛暗"
      ],
      "text": "㕶笃个星贼种！爹多娘少个格？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902172_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902172",
      "scene_id": "70902172_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
